101-279b @##/ /'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa'i gzungs/ bcom ldan 'das ma yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la phyag 'tshal lo/ /tad+ya thA/ o~M pradz+nyA pradz+nye/ pradz+nyA a pa b+hA se/ pradz+nyA ba lo ka ti sarba d+harma an+d+ha kA ra bid+ha ma ni/ sid+d+he su sid+d+he/ sid+d+h+yan+tu mAM b+ha ga ba ti/ sarba dz+nyA na san+d+ha ri/ b+ha ga ba ti bats+tshe la/ pra sa ra d+he ha sta ma ma su ka ra/ sid+d+hi sid+d+hi/ bud+d+ha bud+d+ha/ kaM pa kaM pa/ pA la pA la/ d+ha ra d+ha ra/ ba ra ba ra/ gardza gardza/ A gats+tsha A gats+tsha/ b+ha ga ba ti mA bi

101-280a laM ba swA hA/ 'di bzung bas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa gzung bar 'gyur ro/ /las kyi sgrib pa thams cad byang bar 'gyur ro/ /'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa'i gzungs rdzogs so//
